title: My Post will not show up!!!
body: Ok, before like 3 weeks i made a post On Story Art & Sound with the title All Skins Based On Lore (or something like that) But im trying to search it and nothing shows up can someone help me?

replies.body:
The link to your post about Skins based on lore can be found [HERE](http://boards.na.leagueoflegends.com/en/c/story-art/s0WR5Pzo-skin-lore).

You can always see your own posts by looking at your own Boards Profile. Let me know if you have any questions.

Oh Silly me thanks for helping me out and sorry if i wasted your time with such vapid problem
